  16,79,"alm yanzur almushrikun 'iilaa altayr mdhllat lltyran fi alhawa' bayn alsama' wal'ard bi'amr allh? ma yumsikuhuna ean alwqwe 'iilaa hu subhanah bima khalaqh lha, waqdrha elyh. 'iina fi dhalik altdhlyl wal'imsak ladlalat liqawm yuminun bima yarawnah min al'adilat ealaa qudrat allh"
